He looked to the others. The idea had one problem. The DrillBit and
DarkFate wanted an alliance with the Alliance. DB wasn't sure what
Killfest thought.
"A momement for us do discuss, please."
He walked off a little bit, and motioned for Killfest and DarkFate to
follow.
